## âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/YourUsername/AI-Writing-Assistant.git
   cd AI-Writing-Assistant
Install dependencies

Backend:

bash
Copy code
cd backend
